DophinAttack on the news

Our work "DolphinAttack" has been featured on MIT Technology Review, Zhejiang University front page, BBC, Wired, Forbes, Scientific American Chinese version, IBM Security Intelligence, Fortune, etc.

Research Interests


My interests are in the areas of IoT security and mobile sensing, especially for the security of voice controllable systems and machine learning.

  • IoT Security: Voice Control System, Industry Control System, Smart Grid

  • Machine Learning Security

  • Mobile Sensing
